# Trading System API Tests
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code
# Press Ctrl+Alt+R to execute a request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4101
@apiKey = your-api-key-here

### Health Check - Basic
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/healthz

### Health Check - Detailed
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/healthz?detailed=true

### Get System Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metrics

### Get Current Signals
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/signals
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### EA Bridge - Get Sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/broker/bridge/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### EA Bridge - Get Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/broker/bridge/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### EA Bridge - Get Signal (MT5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/broker/bridge/mt5/signal/get
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### EA Bridge - Connect Session (MT5)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/broker/bridge/mt5/session/connect
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "accountNumber": "12345678",
  "serverName": "MetaQuotes-Demo",
  "version": "1.0.0"
}
